      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        392.39,
        511.45,
        401.39
      ],
      "text": "Op 18 november 2022 heeft UWV uw verzoek om informatie op grond van de Wet open overheid",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        403.31,
        417.25,
        412.31
      ],
      "text": "(hierna: Woo) ontvangen. Hierbij ontvangt u onze beslissing op uw verzoek.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        426.11,
        121.61,
        435.11
      ],
      "text": "Beslissing",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        437.03,
        515.67,
        446.03
      ],
      "text": "UWV heeft besloten de aangetroffen documenten met de door u verzochte informatie openbaar te",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "page": 1,
      "bbox": [
        70.82,
        447.95,
        104.55,
        456.95
      ],
      "text": "maken.",
      "source": "text"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
